              thus creating wealth for its stakeholders.
KPL has focused on seizing the business opportunities in the most buoyant and vibrant sectors of the economy such as Real Estate, Investments and International Trading of Exports & Imports. The core concentration of Kothari Products Ltd., is now on the business of Real Estate, Investments and International Trade


 






 


 















 


