About Kothari Petrochemicals
 
A part of the renowned HC Kothari Group, we are the largest producer of premium quality Polybutene in India. Since our founding in 1990, the company has enjoyed a strong market position in India with a rapidly growing brand across the globe that represents quality, customer responsiveness, dependability and a commitment to the environment.
In the financial year 2007-2008, Kothari Petrochemicals commissioned a second plant in Manali that doubled our production capacity to 22,000 MT per annum in order to supply Polybutene worldwide. We have offices in Chennai, Manali, Mumbai and Belgium, and supply to customers in 20 countries around the world.


 
 
 



 




 


    
